						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājarāja I. Year 23 and 33rd day: A.D. 1009.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged and unfinished. Registers a royal order of king Rājarāja I issued while he was present on the western side of the southern palace at Tīkkālivallam. The purport of the royal document is not known since that portion in the inscription is lost.</p>						

